Nigerian disc jockey, Florence Otedola, popularly known as DJ Cuppy, has urged her fans to be patient with her as younger sister, Temi Otedola is set to marry Nigerian singer, Oluwatosin Ajibade, aka Mr Eazi. Recall that Temi announced her engagement to his long time lover and boyfriend on Sunday in a post on her official Instagram page. While reacting to their engagement, DJ Cuppy informed her fans in a tweet to be patient with her as she would get married in due time. She tweeted, “Congrats to all Temi’s Teddies. My Cupcakes, be patient o LMAO.” Congrats to all Temi’s Teddies My Cupcakes  -be patient o LMAO